videos.description: J.D. Moore catches the pass and then fumbles after a big hit to give Texas A&M great field position.
videos.headline: LSU fumbles on first play

videos.description: Justin McMillan picks off Nick Starkel and gets the ball back for the Tigers.
videos.headline: LSU gets it right back

videos.description: Kevin Toliver forces the fumble and Donnie Alexander returns it all the way to the 23-yard line.
videos.headline: Tigers get another takeaway

videos.description: D.J. Chark makes a great over-the-shoulder catch for the 49-yard completion.
videos.headline: LSU's Chark hauls in tough grab

videos.description: Danny Etling fires a strike to a diving Russell Gage for an LSU touchdown.
videos.headline: Gage makes diving catch for TD
LSU VS TA&M

videos.description: Odell Beckham Jr. says he played in an LSU offense that ran the ball on every down and envies the Tigers current offensive system.
videos.headline: OBJ says people think he is a selfish player

videos.description: Nick Starkel drops it in Christian Kirk's breadbasket to set them up in the red zone.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Starkel drops a dime to Kirk

videos.description: Trayveon Williams gets the edge and finds the end zone for Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Williams puts Aggies on the board with rushing TD

videos.description: LSU's Ed Orgeron says his field goal kicking situation is what it is and his team needs to play a full 60 minutes.
videos.headline: Coach O says Tigers need to be better in red zone

videos.description: Nick Starkel finds a wide open Damion Ratley for a touchdown to make it a one-score game.
videos.headline: Aggies score on 45-yard strike

videos.description: LSU defender breaks on the ball and makes a diving interception for the Tigers.
videos.headline: LSU picks off Starkel again

videos.description: Clyde Edwards-Helaire breaks multiple tackles as he rumbles down to the one-yard line.
videos.headline: LSU's Edwards-Helaire bounces off defenders

videos.description: Derrius Guice uses a strong second effort for the rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: LSU's Guice powers his way in for TD

videos.description: Nick Starkel drops it in to Christian Kirk in the corner of the end zone for a 10-yard score.
videos.headline: Kirk hauls in Aggies TD

videos.description: J.D. Moore leaps over the defender and runs in for the 10-yard touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Moore hurdles his way in for Tigers TD

videos.description: Darrel Williams gets the direct snap and takes off for a huge gain.
videos.headline: LSU's Williams rips off 77-yard run

videos.description: Danny Etling throws to D.J. Chark on a slant to extend the LSU lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Etling hits Chark for LSU TD

videos.description: Devin White picks off the pass and a scuffle ensues on the sideline after the play, Texas A&M's Clyde Chriss is ejected for his role in the fight.
videos.headline: Tempers flare after LSU INT

videos.description: Ed Orgeron is proud of how his team finished the season and wants his running back Derrius Guice to come back for one more year.
videos.headline: Coach O is proud of his team's performance

videos.description: LSU's Derrius Guice rushed for 127 yards in what may be his final game in Tiger Stadium.
videos.headline: Guice says he is undecided about future

videos.description: Jordan Rodgers says Coach Ed Orgeron's coaching style sparked the Tigers' turnaround after their loss to Troy.
videos.headline: LSU completes their amazing turnaround with a sound victory against Texas A&M
